    <item>
      <title>Groups</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/groups/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/groups/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;groups-view-for-tyk-ai-portal&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Groups View for Tyk AI Portal&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#groups-view-for-tyk-ai-portal&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Groups View allows administrators to manage role-based access control by organizing users into groups. Groups define permissions and access levels across the portal, enabling streamlined user management.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;table-overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;Table Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#table-overview&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The groups are displayed in a tabular format with the following columns:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ID&lt;/strong&gt;:&#xA;A unique identifier assigned to each group for easy reference.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Name&lt;/strong&gt;:&#xA;The name of the group, describing its role or purpose (e.g., &amp;ldquo;Solutions Architects,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;Customer Support&amp;rdquo;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Llms</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/llms/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/llms/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-llms-vendor-list&#34;&gt;&#xA;  The LLMs Vendor List&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#the-llms-vendor-list&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;LLMs View&lt;/strong&gt; provides administrators with an overview of the Large Language Model (LLM) vendors integrated into the portal. This section allows for managing the LLMs available for use in Chat Room features and the AI Gateway. Below is a breakdown of the features and data displayed:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;table-overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;Table Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#table-overview&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The table displays the following columns:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Name&lt;/strong&gt;:&#xA;The name of the LLM vendor or model (e.g., Anthropic, OpenAI GPT-4o, VLLM).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
