    <item>
      <title>Users</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/users/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/users/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;users-list-view-for-tyk-ai-portal&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Users List View for Tyk AI Portal&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#users-list-view-for-tyk-ai-portal&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Users List View provides administrators with an overview of all registered users on the platform. This interface allows for managing users&amp;rsquo; access and permissions. Below is a detailed explanation of its components:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;table-overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;Table Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#table-overview&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The table contains user-specific data displayed in rows and organized into the following columns:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ID&lt;/strong&gt;:&#xA;A unique identifier assigned to each user for easy referencing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
